content: Great game. Very simple but satisfying gameplay, practically infinite content, great artstyle/graphics, always getting updates, and all around one of the best games you can find on the app store. More importantly, we all know how bad ads are on this god-forsaken store. This game has very few. Don't get me wrong if you watch the optional ones you could spend hours on ads, but as for forced ads, you get one every two games and they're always five seconds or less. (Or you can use airplane mode..)
